Value vs Predicted
We compare AQ prediction based on weather data with actual values measured after national lockdown has been implemented in various countries.

div.div:
Fitting models
We use Gradient Boosting Method to model pollutant concentration based on weather and climatic data.
Predictors include all weather and climatic variables indicated above with 2-day lags (i.e. current day, 1-day & 2-day lag)
One model is fitted per station and pollutant.
